Witty Repartee	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When engaged in melee combat, the buccaneer keeps up a steady stream of banter that can soon infuriate an unbalanced opponent. From 3rd level onwards, the buccaneer may use his witty repartee class feature in conjunction with a full attack combat option. Both he and one opponent make opposed Will checks, with the buccaneer using his class level as a bonus modifier. If the buccaneer is successful, his opponent suffers a -2 morale penalty to all attacks rolls until the start of the buccaneer's next round.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Witty Repartee																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Superb Seaman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 4th level, the buccaneer becomes so in tune with his ship and the sea that he may add +2 competence bonus to all Seamanship checks. At 8th level, he receives a further +2 competence bonus on all Seamanship checks.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Superb Seaman				DEFINE:SuperbSeamanBonus|0					BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Seamanship)|SuperbSeamanBonus|TYPE=Competence	BONUS:VAR|SuperbSeamanBonus|2	BONUS:VAR|SuperbSeamanBonus|2|PREVARGTEQ:BuccaneerLVL,8															SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
