Rope Fighting	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 7th level, a buccaneer has become so proficient at fighting along masts and in the rigging that he may retain his Dexterity bonus to his Armor Class when engaged in combat. In addition, enemies will gain no bonus to hit when he is in such a position. The buccaneer will still lose his Dexterity bonus in other circumstances, such as being flst-footed.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Rope Fighting																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
