Inspire Crew	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ReaverClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Reavers are skilled not only in boarding actions, but also in encouraging their crews to fight to best effect. A crew led by a reaver are likely to believe they are invincible and will never be defeated. From 2nd level, the reaver grants the crew he leads the morale bonus listed to their attack and damage rolls (+%1). This only applies during boarding action and if the reaver flees or is killed during the battle, this morale bonus will immediately be converted into a morale penalty, affecting the crew's attack and damage rolls (-%1).|InspireCrewBonus	KEY:Reaver ~ Inspire Crew				DEFINE:InspireCrewBonus|0					BONUS:VAR|InspireCrewBonus|(ReaverLVL+2)/4																	SORTKEY:Class_Reaver	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
