Instil Fear	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ReaverClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the reaver reaches 4th level, he gains the extraordinary ability to cast Fear as a free action %1/day. This ability may be used during boarding action and the reaver must perform some dramatic and morale building action in view of his crew and his enemies in the action it is used. This ability has a range of 5-ft per class level (%2) of the reaver and all within the range will be frightened for 1d6 rouds. Those who passes a will save (DC 10+reaver's class level + reaver's CHA, DC %3) will merely be shaken for this time.|InstillFearTimes|InstillFearRadius|InstillFearDC	KEY:Reaver ~ Instil Fear				DEFINE:InstillFearDC|0	DEFINE:InstillFearTimes|0	DEFINE:InstillFearRadius|0			BONUS:VAR|InstillFearDC|10+ReaverLVL+CHA	BONUS:VAR|InstillFearDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Instil Fear)	BONUS:VAR|InstillFearTimes|1	BONUS:VAR|InstillFearRadius|5*ReaverLVL						ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Instil Fear								SORTKEY:Class_Reaver	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
